name: Jockstrap
description:
This is a LoRA trained on classic jockstraps. Primarily, the Bike Vintage Throwback, Bike white classic 7110 vintage jockstrap. After much experimentation, this version now allows you to use different characters and body types. Trained on 512x512 images, and white, yellow, and red jockstraps.

Note:

  • Works best with controlnet openpose.

  • It leans towards white backgrounds. Add parenthesis to your locations to get them to work. e.g. (forest in the background:1.1)

  • Ass/From behind is not reliable at all and isn't the focus of this LoRA.

  • Dial the weight down to 0.8 to allow the checkpoint you're using to have more of an influence on the outputs.

Keywords: dirty used white/red/yellow jockstrap with a bulge, ass, from behind

Example prompt: photo of a man wearing a dirty used white jockstrap with a bulge

Optional negative prompts: white background, tattoos, close up photo, blurry, ass

See other people's prompts and results below and post your own!
